<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Not-Null on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/not-null/</link><description>Recent content in Not-Null on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/not-null/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] SQL Column Cannot Be Null Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/sql/null-constraint/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/sql/null-constraint/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="sql-column-cannot-be-null-error-fix"&gt;SQL Column Cannot Be Null Error Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when an INSERT or UPDATE tries to set a NOT NULL column to NULL. The message reads: &lt;code&gt;Column 'X' cannot be null&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NOT NULL constraints require that a column always contains a value. If no value is provided or the source expression evaluates to NULL, the database rejects the operation. This commonly happens with missing data, failed JOINs, or unset application defaults.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>SQLite Constraint Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/sqlite-constraint-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/sqlite-constraint-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="sqlite-constraint-error"&gt;SQLite Constraint Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A SQLite constraint error occurs when an INSERT or UPDATE operation violates a table constraint. Common constraints include PRIMARY KEY, UNIQUE, NOT NULL, and CHECK.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Duplicate PRIMARY KEY value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;UNIQUE constraint violation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NOT NULL constraint on required column&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CHECK constraint failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="handle-duplicate-key-errors"&gt;Handle Duplicate Key Errors&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Use INSERT OR IGNORE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IGNORE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users (id, name) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Alice&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Use INSERT OR REPLACE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;REPLACE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users (id, name) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Alice&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Use ON CONFLICT (SQLite 3.24+)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users (id, name) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Alice&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt; CONFLICT(id) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DO&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;UPDATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SET&lt;/span&gt; name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; excluded.name;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-existing-constraints"&gt;Check Existing Constraints&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;schema&lt;/span&gt; users
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Shows CREATE TABLE with constraints
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="handle-null-values"&gt;Handle NULL Values&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Ensure required fields are provided
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users (id, name) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NULL&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Error: NOT NULL constraint failed: users.name
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-trycatch-in-application-code"&gt;Use TRY/CATCH in Application Code&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; sqlite3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; conn&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;execute(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;INSERT INTO users VALUES (1, &amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;)&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;except&lt;/span&gt; sqlite3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;IntegrityError &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; e:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Constraint error: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;e&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-check-constraints"&gt;Check CHECK Constraints&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Table with CHECK constraint
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; products (
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; id INTEGER &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PRIMARY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;KEY&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; price REAL &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CHECK&lt;/span&gt;(price &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- INSERT INTO products VALUES (1, -10);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Error: CHECK constraint failed: products
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; users (
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; id INTEGER &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PRIMARY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;KEY&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; email TEXT &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;UNIQUE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NOT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NULL&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;alice@example.com&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;alice@example.com&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Error: UNIQUE constraint failed: users.email
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/sqlite-syntax-error/"&gt;Syntax Error&lt;/a&gt; — SQL syntax error&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/type-mismatch3/"&gt;Type Error&lt;/a&gt; — type mismatch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>